        flask-json-errorhandler
        =======================
        
        Register json errorhandlers for a flask REST server
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: python
        
            from flask import Flask
        
            from flask_json_errorhandler import init_errorhandler(app)
        
        
            def create_app():
                app = Flask(__name__)
                init_errorhandler(app)
        
        Testing
        -------
        
        .. code:: python
        
            python setup.py test
        
